desc_long								关于这款游戏							Following a successful Kickstarter that gathered more than 3,500 backers in 2013, Faeria was revamped to make it closer to our vision of “easy to learn, hard to master”. Faeria combines the core values of Strategy Card Games together with a Living Board, giving you the ability to shape the board as you play to create mind-blowing strategies. Each game of Faeria is not only unique, beautiful and fast-paced but also highly competitive with upcoming features such as an observer mode and integrated tournaments. Faeria's Early Access Bundle helps you kickstart your experience by giving you access to: The Game 20 Booster Packs 10 Arena Tickets Early Access Exclusive Avatar and Orb						
